Windswept Description

Overhauling Minecraft's Visuals, making minecraft more cosy.

Features like:

Wind and Wind Reactions
Water based effects, Cascades, Wakes, Tides and ripples
Clouds Overhaul
Weather Overhaul
Ambient sounds

All just for you! No server install needed!

